, education and youth work. I have a BA (Hons) in Education and MA in Health Promotion. I currently work on a self-employed basis developing and providing high quality training, developing educational resources and conducting needs assessments and small scale research. I also directly deliver lessons and workshops to young people in schools, colleges and youth settings.I have been an Associate Trainer for the FPA for the past 8 years. I developed and deliver a one day course \'Fantasy Vs Reality: the impact and influence of pornography on young people\'s sexual attitudes and behaviour\'. I have also co-written and deliver \'The Pleasure Principle\' and \'Young people, sex and alcohol\' for the FPA. If you are interested in booking on these courses, visit <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.fpa.org.uk\\/training\\\">www.fpa.org.uk\\/training<br><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"myBlockUrl\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\"}},\"57\":{\"type\":\"twoTextColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockLeftColumnHeading\":\"Course participant, Brighton, March 2014\",\"myBlockLeftColumn\":\"<p>\'<em>Great session! Very knowledgeable trainer!\'<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"myBlockRightColumnHeading\":\"FVR, London, 2013\",\"myBlockRightColumn\":\"<p><em>\'Liz provided a very interesting and engaging session and I now feel more confident in delivering my sex and relationships work, especially in tackling issues relating to pornography<\\/em>\'<br><\\/p>\",\"textRowNo\":\"textRow1\"}},\"58\":{\"type\":\"twoTextColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockLeftColumnHeading\":\"FVR, Dorset, Sept 2012\",\"myBlockLeftColumn\":\"<p><em>\'An excellent course which was well presented and interactive\'<\\/em><br><\\/p>\",\"myBlockRightColumnHeading\":\"FVR, London 2012\",\"myBlockRightColumn\":\"<p><em>\'Liz was clearly very knowledgeable and created a safe, boundaried environment to explore the issues within\'<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"textRowNo\":\"textRow1\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"contactMe\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"contactMe\":\