 behaviour of young people.<br>&nbsp;<br>The pack contains 5 lesson plans, differentiated for Key Stage 3 (14-15 yr olds) and Key Stage 4 (15-16 yr olds).<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"\\/assets\\/images\\/me-2016.JPG#asset:119\\\"><br><\\/p>\",\"mainContentText\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\"}}}}}', '2016-09-20 19:34:08', '2016-09-20 19:34:08', '62be85ea-0117-4c53-8211-c19bc941b344'),
