 ('195', '8', '5', '1', 'en_gb', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"PSHE\",\"slug\":\"pshe\",\"postDate\":1441133320,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"7\":{\"55\":{\"type\":\"singleBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockHeading\":\"PSHE\",\"myBlockImage\":[\"61\"],\"myBlockUrl\":\"\",\"myBlockTextboxText\":\"<p>I am experienced at delivering PSHE lessons on a range of topics, including mental health & well-being; sex & relationships; the impact and influence of pornography; the media & sexualisation; anti-bullying; stress management; nutrition; physical activity; sexuality\\/challenging homophobia as well as money management. I can deliver one off lessons, a series of lessons, organise a PSHE day \\u2018team\\u2019 delivery with a trusted team of colleagues or present at assemblies. Please contact me to discuss your requirements.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>I work to up to date good practice and guidance on PSHE delivery in association with (links to PSHE Association \\/ Sex Ed Forum etc)<\\/p>\",\"mainContentText\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"pairedBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"leftColumnHeading\":\"Consultancy Work\",\"leftColumnImage\":\"\",\"leftColumnTextboxText\":\"\",\"leftColumnText\":\"<p>Through my consultancy work I am available to plan, deliver and evaluate presentations,&nbsp;seminars, workshops or training courses (either half day or whole day) to practitioners, these include:<\\/p><ul><the influence=\\\"\\\" and=\\\"\\\" impact=\\\"\\\" of=\\\"\\\" pornography=\\\"\\\" broader=\\\"\\\" sexualisaion=\\\"\\\" on=\\\"\\\" young=\\\"\\\" people\'s=\\\"\\\" sexual=\\\"\\\" health=\\\"\\\" (including=\\\"\\\" strategies=\\\"\\\" practical=\\\"\\\" ways=\\\"\\\" we=\\\"\\\" can=\\\"\\\" respond)=\\\"\\\"><li>The influence and impact of pornography and broader sexualisaion on young people\'s sexual health (including strategies and practical ways we can respond)<\\/li><li>Sex, Drugs 