 ('222', '42', '2', '1', 'en_gb', '46', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"About\",\"slug\":\"liz\",\"postDate\":1450032180,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"7\":{\"56\":{\"type\":\"singleBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockHeading\":\"About\",\"myBlockImage\":\"\",\"myBlockUrl\":\"\",\"myBlockTextboxText\":\"<p><img src=\\\"\\/assets\\/images\\/me-2016.JPG#asset:119:url\\\">I am a self-employed educator, trainer, youth worker and facilitator. I have 15 years\\u2019 experience of working across a variety of areas and subjects including Public Health & Health Promotion; Behaviour Change; Motivational Interviewing; Youth work, Education and Social care covering a range of issues relating to health & well-being, specifically sexual health; drugs & alcohol and mental health and well-being. I plan and deliver presentations, training courses, workshops and lessons. I also produce teaching resources and health promotion materials, conduct needs assessments and small scale pieces of research. I am based in Sussex, but also work across the UK.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>I am a member of MINT (Motivational Interviewing Network of Trainers) <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.motivationalinterviewing.org\\\">www.motivationalinterviewing.o...<\\/a><br><br>As well as my extensive work with practitioners, I also work directly with young people, delivering lessons, workshops and 1-1 sessions. I currently work with The Young People\'s Centre in Brighton and the wider Youth Collective <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.brightonandhoveyouthcollective.org.uk\\\">www.brightonandhoveyouthcollec...<\\/a> This is important to me to ensure my training courses are kept in line with current practice and the challenges and possibilities in this work.<br><br>My background is in the NHS, education and youth work. I have a BA (Hons) in Education and MA in Health Promotion. I currently work on a self-employed basis developing and providing high quality training, developing educational resources and conducting needs assessments and small scale research. I also directly deliver lessons and workshops to young people in schools, colleges and youth settings.I have been an Associate Trainer for the FPA for the past 8 years. I developed and deliver a one day course \'Fantasy Vs Reality: the impact and influence of pornography on young people\'s sexual attitudes and behaviour\'. I have also co-written and deliver \'The Pleasure Principle\' and \'Young people, sex and alcohol\' for the FPA. If you are interested in booking on these courses, visit <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.fpa.org.uk\\/training\\\">www.fpa.org.uk\\/training<br><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"mainContentText\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\"}},\"125\":{\"type\":\"pairedBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"leftColumnHeading\":\"Course participant, Brighton, March 2014\",\"leftColumnImage\":\"\",\"leftColumnTextboxText\":\"\",\"leftColumnText\":\"<p>\'<em>Great session! Very knowledgeable trainer!\'<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"leftColumnImageUrl\":\"\",\"rightColumnHeading\":\"FVR, London, 2013\",\"rightColumnImage\":\"\",\"rightColumnTextboxText\":\"\",\"rightColumnText\":\"<p><em>\'Liz provided a very interesting and engaging session and I now feel more confident in delivering my sex and relationships work, especially in tackling issues relating to pornography<\\/em>\'<\\/p>\",\"rightColumnImageUrl\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\"}},\"57\":{\"type\":\"twoTextColumns\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"LeftColumnHeading\":\"Course participant, Brighton, March 2014\",\"LeftColumnText\":\"<p>\'<em>Great session! Very knowledgeable trainer!\'<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"RightColumnHeading\":\"FVR, London, 2013\",\"RightColumnText\":\"<p><em>\'Liz provided a very interesting and engaging session and I now feel more confident in delivering my sex and relationships work, especially in tackling issues relating to pornography<\\/em>\'<br><\\/p>\",\"tags\":\"\"}},\"126\":{\"type\":\"pairedBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"leftC